manifest.Bundle-Description: The Netty project is an effort to provide an asynchronous event-driven    network application framework and tools for rapid development of    maintainable high performance and high scalability protocol servers and    clients.  In other words, Netty is a NIO client server framework which    enables quick and easy development of network applications such as protocol    servers and clients. It greatly simplifies and streamlines network    programming such as TCP and UDP socket server.
